ed="T" n="0722a27"/><persName key="A000993">釋般若</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000055418">罽賓國</placeName>人也。貌質魁梧，執戒嚴整，<lb
ed="T" n="0722a28"/>在<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042189">京師</ref>，充義學<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g395"/>沙門。<persName key="A002120">憲宗</persName>敦崇佛門，深思<lb
ed="T" n="0722a29"/>翻譯，奈何有事于<placeName key="PL000000035107">蜀部</placeName><ptr type="glossary" target="#g2176"/>，<persName key="A009181">劉闢</persName>阻命<ptr target="#n416"/>，<persName key="A009182">王承宗</persName><pb ed="T" n="0722b" xml:id="T50.2061.0722b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0722b01"/>未平，朝廷多故<ptr target="#n417"/>。至<date from-iso="+0810-02-12" key="j20169492017302" to-iso="+0811-01-31"><name>元和</name>五年庚寅</date>，詔工部<lb
ed="T" n="0722b02"/>侍郎<persName key="A009183">歸登</persName>、<persName key="A009184">孟簡</persName>、<persName key="A009185">劉伯芻</persName>、<persName key="A009186">蕭俛</persName>等。就<placeName key="PL000000042317">醴泉寺</placeName>譯<lb
ed="T" n="0722b03"/>出經八卷，號《本生心地觀》<ptr target="#n976"/>，此之<name>梵</name>夾乃<persName key="A002146">高宗</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0722b04"/>朝<placeName key="PL000000048734">師子國</placeName>所進者，寫畢進上。<ref type="person" target="#A002120">帝</ref>覽有勅，「<ref type="person" target="#A002120">朕</ref><lb
ed="T" n="0722b05"/>願為序」。尋<anchor xml:id="beg0722sgsz5"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>頌</sic><corr>頒</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0722sgsz5"/>下其文，冠于經首<ptr target="#n977"/>，<ref target="#A000993" type="person">三藏</ref>賜帛，<lb
ed="T" n="0722b06"/>證義<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g54"/>諸沙門錫賚有差。<anchor xml:id="beg0722sgsz6"/>先<anchor xml:id="end0722sgsz6"/>於<date notBefore-iso="+0785-02-18" key="j20078242015139" notAfter-iso="+0805-02-28"><name>貞元</name>中</date>譯《華<lb
ed="T" n="0722b07"/>嚴經》<ptr target="#n223"/>後分四十卷。此蓋<placeName key="PL000000048336">烏荼國</placeName>王所進者，于<lb
ed="T" n="0722b08"/>時而賜紫衣。後<date notBefore-iso="+0847-02-10" key="j20304612035523" notAfter-iso="+0860-12-20"><name>大中</name>中</date>，<persName key="A009180"><persName>法寶大師</persName><persName>玄暢</persName></persName>奏請<lb
ed="T" n="0722b09"/>入藏焉。</p>
